      "start": 117.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 121.9000015258789,
      "text": "All after the summer's end",
      "start": 118.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 124.27999877929688,
      "text": "Chains they tacitly lift me up",
      "start": 121.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 126.18000030517578,
      "text": "It's like a panic attack",
      "start": 124.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 129.5399932861328,
      "text": "I erupt, emotions and dreams and life and what it seems",
      "start": 126.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 132.33999633789062,
      "text": "Do I get another shot at what we seem?",
      "start": 129.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 135.05999755859375,
      "text": "Then I understand it's hard that you breathe",
      "start": 132.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 138.55999755859375,
      "text": "Yeah, it's right that you waste",
      "start": 136.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 141.3800048828125,
      "text": "If you sit there not being true",
      "start": 138.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 144.05999755859375,
      "text": "Turn your own faith in place",
      "start": 141.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 147.74000549316406,
      "text": "I'll see you then",
      "start": 145.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 152.4600067138672,
      "text": "There's more to life than any other",
      "start": 148.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 156.39999389648438,
      "text": "Thing that you could ever dream of",
      "start": 152.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 158.74000549316406,
      "text": "Where I'm being true",
      "start": 156.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 161.25999450683594,
      "text": "Where I'm wanting to",
      "start": 158.74000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 165.25999450683594,
      "text": "Dream with me a little louder",
      "start": 162.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 168.24000549316406,
      "text": "There's more to life",
      "start": 166.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 172.63999938964844,
      "text": "There's more to life than the dark to finding grey",
      "start": 168.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 175.6999969482422,
      "text": "A matter of where you just start",
      "start": 172.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 177.52000427246094,
      "text": "To look left",
      "start": 175.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 180.10000610351562,
      "text": "And you're here",
      "start": 178.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 182.25999450683594,
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 181.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 186.3800048828125,
      "text": "That's how the end of the summer feels",
      "start": 182.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 187.4600067138672,
      "text": "With you",
      "start": 186.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 190.74000549316406,
      "text": "You're looking great in that tan",
      "start": 187.4600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 194.6199951171875,
      "text": "Your bathing suit's on fire, baby",
      "start": 191.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 200.25999450683594,
      "text": "I can't stop but to misbehave",
      "start": 194.82000732421875
    }
  ],
